<P>
<s docid="LA052089-0075" num="40" wdcount="14"> Photo, Imelda Marcos at Honolulu hospital where her husband, Ferdinand, is clinging to life.</s>
<s docid="LA052089-0075" num="41" wdcount="2"> Associated Press</s>
